    <id>http://fireinside.me/blog/2012/08/08/unicode-in-irb</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>If you&#8217;re having problems with unicode characters in IRB from ruby compiled with rbenv, do this:</p>

<pre>$ brew install readline
